						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone set up in Kallēśvara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Ānanda, Kārtika śu. 12,</hi> records the death of a hero (name lost), who was the son of <hi rend="bold">Bōjaya-Nāyaka.</hi> The characters are of about the <hi rend="bold">14th century A.D.</hi></p>						

